  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nWebSockets throw System.Net.WebSockets.WebSocketException (2): The WebSocket is in an invalid state ('Aborted') for this operation. Valid states are: 'Open, CloseReceived, CloseSent'\r\nwhen a client disconnects forcibly.\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce**\r\nSteps to reproduce the behavior:\r\n1. Connect to JSON RPC using web sockets\r\n2. Close the client forcibly (for example by killing the process)\r\n",
